  {
    "title": "L'importance de la performance web en 2026",
    "slug": "importance-performance-web",
    "status": "published",
    "excerpt": "Un site rapide est un site qui convertit. Decouvrez pourquoi la performance web est plus cruciale que jamais et comment l'ameliorer.",
    "category": "Technique",
    "tags": ["performance", "SEO", "technique"],
    "author": "admin",
    "published_at": "2026-03-05",
    "content": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "section",
          "id": "post3-content",
          "props": {
            "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
            "paddingTop": 40,
            "paddingBottom": 40,
            "paddingLeft": 24,
            "paddingRight": 24,
            "maxWidth": 700,
            "centered": true
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "post3-p1",
              "props": {
                "content": "<p style='color:#334155;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;'>Selon Google, 53% des visiteurs mobiles quittent un site qui met plus de 3 secondes a charger. La performance n'est pas un luxe technique, c'est un imperatif business.</p>"
              },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "spacer",
              "id": "post3-sp1",
              "props": { "height": 24 },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "id": "post3-h1",
              "props": {
                "text": "L'impact sur le SEO",
                "level": 2,
                "alignment": "left",
                "color": "#0f172a"
              },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "post3-p2",
              "props": {
                "content": "<p style='color:#334155;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;'>Les Core Web Vitals (LCP, INP, CLS) sont desormais des criteres de classement officiels de Google. Un site performant est un site mieux reference. Les trois metriques cles a surveiller :</p>"
              },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "spacer",
              "id": "post3-sp2",
              "props": { "height": 16 },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "list",
              "id": "post3-list",
              "props": {
                "items": [
                  "LCP (Largest Contentful Paint) : le plus gros element visible doit charger en moins de 2.5 secondes",
                  "INP (Interaction to Next Paint) : les interactions doivent repondre en moins de 200ms",
                  "CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift) : les elements de la page ne doivent pas bouger de maniere inattendue"
                ],
                "style": "unordered"
              },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "spacer",
              "id": "post3-sp3",
              "props": { "height": 24 },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "id": "post3-h2",
              "props": {
                "text": "Les leviers d'optimisation",
                "level": 2,
                "alignment": "left",
                "color": "#0f172a"
              },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "post3-p3",
              "props": {
                "content": "<p style='color:#334155;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;'>Optimiser les images (formats modernes comme WebP, lazy loading), minimiser le CSS et JavaScript, utiliser un CDN, mettre en cache intelligemment, et choisir un hebergement de qualite. Chaque milliseconde compte.</p>"
              },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "spacer",
              "id": "post3-sp4",
              "props": { "height": 24 },
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "type": "blockquote",
              "id": "post3-quote",
              "props": {
                "content": "La vitesse n'est pas une fonctionnalite, c'est LE fonctionnalite.",
                "citation": "Tobias Lutke, CEO de Shopify"
              },
              "children": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "taxonomies": {
      "categories": ["technique"],
      "tags": ["performance", "seo", "technique"]
    }
  }
